OL,3,CGreggs to open international shop at
OL,4,CTenerife South airport
OL,6,FHolidaymakers will be able to buy a
OL,7,FGreggs sausage roll at Tenerife South
OL,8,Fairport from later this month when the
OL,9,Fbaker opens its only international
OL,10,Foutlet.
OL,12,FGreggs last operated shops abroad in
OL,13,FBelgium in 2008, but said Tenerife was
OL,14,F"the ideal location to test spreading
OL,15,Four wings in an overseas setting".
OL,26,@vD@AOUwD@aO]
