OL,3,CGreggs to open international shop at
OL,4,CTenerife South airport
OL,6,FWhile the exact date for the opening
OL,7,Fis not yet set, Greggs said the shop
OL,8,Fin the international departures area
OL,9,Fof the airport will stock a range of
OL,10,Fbakes, rolls and sweet treats, as well
OL,11,Fas freshly-made sandwiches.
OL,13,FA Spanish omelette roll will be
OL,14,Favailable as part of the breakfast
OL,15,Fmenu alongside freshly squeezed orange
OL,16,Fjuice, prepared and bottled in-shop
OL,17,Fdaily, "giving customers a refreshing
OL,18,Ftaste of island life", the baker said.
OL,26,@yD@HOUzD@UO]
