OL,3,CGreggs to open international shop at
OL,4,CTenerife South airport
OL,6,FTenerife South airport welcomes around
OL,7,F13 million holidaymakers every year,
OL,8,Fwith around 50% flying to and from the
OL,9,FUK.
OL,11,FGreggs said the location made it the
OL,12,F"perfect way to round off a trip
OL,13,Fwithout breaking the bank".
OL,15,FThe shop will also offer seating for
OL,16,Fup to 92 customers.
OL,26,@tD@AOUuD@ZO]
