OL,3,CGreggs to open international shop at
OL,4,CTenerife South airport
OL,6,FThe new shop will open in partnership
OL,7,Fwith Lagardere Travel Retail, which
OL,8,Foperates more than 5,000 stores in
OL,9,Fairports, railway stations and other
OL,10,Flocations in over 50 countries
OL,11,Fworldwide.
OL,13,FJavier Cagigal, chief executive of
OL,14,FLagardere Travel Retail Spain and
OL,15,FPortugal, said: "We're delighted to
OL,16,Fpartner with Greggs to bring such a
OL,17,Fwell-loved brand into Tenerife South
OL,18,FAirport for the very first time.
OL,26,@wD@QOU
